==English==
===Etymology===
Named after [[w:New York Yankees|New York Yankees]] baseball player [[w:Lou Gehrig|Lou Gehrig]] (1903-1941), a prominent suffer of the disease.  The disease was known before Gehrig suffered it, his fame led to his name being associated with it.

===Noun===
'''[[Lou]] [[Gehrig]]’s [[disease]]'''

# [[amyotrophic lateral sclerosis|Amyotrophic lateral sclerosis]], a form of [[motor neuron disease]].

